StyleBox[\"2\", \"TR\"]], \",\", StyleBox[\"\[Ellipsis]\", \"TR\"]}], \
\"}\"}]}], \"]\"}]\) makes a nested list with length \
\!\(\*SubscriptBox[StyleBox[\"n\", \"TI\"], StyleBox[\"i\", \"TI\"]]\) at \
level \!\(\*StyleBox[\"i\", \"TI\"]\). \n\!\(\*RowBox[{\"PadLeft\", \"[\", \
StyleBox[\"list\", \"TI\"], \"]\"}]\) pads a ragged array \
\!\(\*StyleBox[\"list\", \"TI\"]\) with zeros to make it full. ", 
